      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found\u2014it\u2019s basically a time capsule! It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is still smelling fresh. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin before someone else snaps it up! \u2728",
