    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the naturally aspirated 3.8L horizontally opposed six-cylinder engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear power band and 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and turn-in response. Meticulously maintained, the borescope inspection shows no scoring, and the DME report confirms zero over-revs in high-load ranges. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster with zero rock chips, while the undercarriage remains concours-clean. This is a turnkey, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 49500.0,
