    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This one-owner gem has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one, preserving its deep, mirror-like finish and original ceramic coating. There isn't a single stone chip, swirl mark, or parking lot ding to be found on its flawless exterior. Inside, the cabin remains in a showroom state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine with no sun exposure, and it still retains that distinctive 'new car' scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive folder of every service record performed exclusively at the original dealership. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions perfectly. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting the obsessive maintenance this vehicle has received. If you are looking for a 'no-excuses' example that represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year, this is the one. A rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its purest, most pristine form.",
